Name: Queen Of Bud Pre Rolls - Shungite - Garlic Kush  2 x 0.5g Pre-rolls
Description: Garlic Kush is the unique, high-THC and high-terpene (more than three per cent) result of combining the cultivars GMO (Garlic Cookies) and OZ Kush from Dark Horse genetics. This pungent bud grows with lighter olive-green hues and goldfish-orange like pistils. These buds have a delicious and funky aroma to them that is a mix of earthy, savoury and spicy, providing a 60-to-40 indica leaning experience. These two 0.5g pre-rolls are hand finished by our highly trained staff (who are fellow consumers) in Sundre, AB, using Konehedz cones and filters, and gently placed in their packaging for minimal agitation.
